results.eventDesc: Adults, please enjoy an evening of stamping, punching, and making handmade greeting cards while visiting with others.  Everything is organized for you so all you need to do is relax and create!  All supplies are provided.
This is an informal group for parents who have lost their children to cancer.  Please join us if you'd like to listen and share with others who have walked a similar journey of bereavement.
